editorialNotes.tagline: Send money abroad the easy way
editorialNotes.standard: Sending money to friends and family in other countries can be a pricey proposition, unless you can find a way to avoid the unfavourable currency exchange rates set by banks. TransferWise uses the standard exchange ratenot your bankswhen you wire money abroad. Its remarkably streamlined and easy to use, especially for frequent transfers, and itll save you plenty of dollars, pounds, euros, zlotywhatever money means to you.
editorialNotes.short: Send money abroad easily and securely.
